<br>
I contacted ARK and asked about it, and they told that MA attacks were moved to missions as a loot. I asked that who was the brainiac behind it, because with my base skills (no implants or anything, plain and pure base skills) I could use literally 2+ times my level QL attacks - BoP for example - and I DEFINATELY cannot get such a mission on my own, even with a team of people at my levels I can't get some QL 130+ or QL 140+ mission and finish it, not to mention that I never even seen any MA attacks drop anywhere in Team Missions. I have seen some pathetic QL MA attacks only as single mission rewards, and these attacks are useless or too weak in most cases. To that the ARK person mumbled something about &quot;checking things&quot; and never was seen again.<br>
<br>
I met a person of my lvl, who showed me the QL 120+ BoP attack. Sweet. I asked where she got it and she said that Borealis Advanced Shop. I asked when and she said &quot;Before 14.2&quot;. I have many friends, on clan side, neutral and omni and asked from them too, to check the stores or recall, when they saw these on sale for the last time. All the answers what I did receive, stated &quot;Before 14.2&quot;.<br>
